WEBVTT

00:00:00.856 --> 00:00:03.531
I would like to begin
with a little experiment.

00:00:03.555 --> 00:00:06.646
In a moment, I'm going to ask
if you would close your eyes

00:00:06.670 --> 00:00:08.142
and see if you can work out

00:00:08.166 --> 00:00:11.076
what emotions you're feeling right now.

00:00:11.100 --> 00:00:13.412
Now, you're not going
to tell anyone or anything.

00:00:13.436 --> 00:00:17.863
The idea is to see how easy
or perhaps hard you find it

00:00:17.887 --> 00:00:20.479
to pinpoint exactly what you're feeling.

00:00:20.503 --> 00:00:23.944
And I thought I'd give you
10 seconds to do this.

00:00:23.968 --> 00:00:25.412
OK?

00:00:25.436 --> 00:00:27.123
Right, let's start.